N2  - The editorial policy of the department on ?Organization Analysis, Performance and Design? encompasses research on the subject of State-Owned Enterprises. The paper ?Managerial Strategic Behavior in State-Owned Enterprises-Business and Political Orientations? by Dr. Zif, of Tel Aviv University follows, and in the research Note ?Performance Evaluation of State-Owned Enterprises: A Process Perspective,? which follows, Professor Aharoni presents the case for conducting research on Stage-Owned Enterprises illustrating the complexity of the various problems and their importance. It is hoped that other research will follow.
